ue to an issue with the AssertJ import? I think the dependency itself is fine, though. I’ll have to look into this further.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_RVeob2migT4m2jVGiVsoCHfW|fc_04ca318d0ca906c2016a27686553288196a10b90bc2a618657", "name": "edit", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/jspapi/jsp-api/2.0-20040521/src/test/java/jspapi/jsp_api/SimpleTagSupportTest.java", "edits": [{"oldText": "import javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.SimpleTagSupport;\n\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n", "newText": "import javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.SimpleTagSupport;\n\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.BeforeAll;\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n"}, {"oldText": "public class SimpleTagSupportTest {\n\n    @Test\n    void findsSimpleTagAncestorByAssignableClass() {\n", "newText": "public class SimpleTagSupportTest {\n\n    @BeforeAll\n    static void reachesJspTagClassLookupBeforeAnyOtherSimpleTagSupportUse() {\n        final SimpleTagSupport parent = new SimpleTagSupport();\n        final SimpleTagSupport child = new SimpleTagSupport();\n        child.setParent(parent);\n\n        assertThat(SimpleTagSupport.findAncestorWithClass(child, SimpleTagSupport.class)).isSameAs(parent);\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void findsSimpleTagAncestorByAssignableClass() {\n"}, {"oldText": "    void findsSimpleTagAncestorByMarkerInterface() {\n        final MarkerTag parent = new MarkerTag();\n        final SimpleTagSupport child = new SimpleTagSupport();\n        child.setParent(parent);\n\n        assertThat(SimpleTagSupport.findAncestorWithClass(child, Marker.class)).isSameAs(parent);\n    }\n\n    private interface Marker {\n", "newText": "    void findsSimpleTagAncestorByMarkerInterface() {\n        final MarkerTag parent = new MarkerTag();\n        final SimpleTagSupport child = new SimpleTagSupport();\n        child.setParent(parent);\n\n        assertThat(SimpleTagSupport.findAncestorWithClass(child, Marker.class)).isSameAs(parent);\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void rejectsLookupClassOutsideJspTagHierarchy() {\n        final SimpleTagSupport child = new SimpleTagSupport();\n\n        assertThat(SimpleTagSupport.findAncestorWithClass(child, String.class)).isNull();\n    }\n\n    private interface Marker {\n"}]}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 413, "output": 2444, "cacheRead": 78336, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 81193, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1780967475985, "responseId": "resp_04ca318d0ca906c2016a276834c8688196b4e8c950a62783de"}}
